HEADWORD: Priestly
<hw>Priest"ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to a priest or
the priesthood; sacerdotal; befitting or becoming a priest; <as>as, the
<ex>priestly</ex> office; a <ex>priestly</ex> farewell.</as></def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

